      "ID": "MC1",
      "Text": "Sustaining the cultural traditions will make the immigrated people keep their cultural identity."
    }
  ],
  "Claims": [
    {
      "ID": "C1",
      "Text": "More people are migrating to other countries than ever before."
    },
    {
      "ID": "C2",
      "Text": "Some people thought that they should follow the local customs in order to integrate into their adopted countries’ cultures."
    },
    {
      "ID": "C3",
      "Text": "It is crucial to keep one’s identity for they need a connection back to their country."
    },
    {
      "ID": "C4",
      "Text": "Fail to create this familiarity makes them felt isolated."
    }
  ],
  "Premises": [
    {
      "ID": "P1",
      "Text": "The last 50 years have seen an increasing number of immigrants to other countries."
    },
    {
      "ID": "P2",
      "Text": "People moved due to a number of reasons, namely better educations or higher salary jobs."
    },
    {
      "ID": "P3",
      "Text": "Maintaining one’s cultural identity is a key important rule to help individuals emerge in the new multicultural environments."
    },
    {
      "ID": "P4",
      "Text": "Many Australians come this day to enjoy the shows, learn about the cultures and admire the diverse values."
    },
    {
      "ID": "P5",
      "Text": "These feedbacks, in turn, help raise one’s pride of their cultures and help people understand each other more."
    },
    {
      "ID": "P6",
      "Text": "Children immigrated to a new country will face social troubles in school with new friends."
    },
    {
      "ID": "P7",
      "Text": "In this new environment, parent should find friends coming from their same country."
    },
    {
      "ID": "P8",
      "Text": "Keeping the cultural traditions in the destination countries is tremendous important."
    }
  ],
