      "ID": "P4",
      "Text": "This was due to the lack of adequate controls by authorities and led to a bad image of Thailand tourism."
    },
    {
      "ID": "P5",
      "Text": "Tourism increasingly creates harms to the natural habitats of the destination appeals."
    },
    {
      "ID": "P6",
      "Text": "The billion visitors per annum has generated immense destruction to the Great Barrier Reef."
    },
    {
      "ID": "P7",
      "Text": "Many marine lives have been endangered, and parts of the reef have become uninhabitable for these marine species."
